<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TolE0102">
<l>ellā veḻuttum veḷippaṭak kiḷantu</l>
<l>colliya paḷḷi yeḻutaru vaḷiyiṟ</l>
<l>piṟappoṭu viṭuvaḻi uṟaḻcci vārat</l>
<l>takatteḻu vaḷiyicai yariṟapa nāṭi</l>
<l>yaḷapiṟ kōṭa lantaṇar maṟaittē</l>
<l>yaḵtiva ṇuvalā teḻuntupuṟat ticaikku</l>
<l>meyteri vaḷiyicai yaḷavunuvaṉ ṟiciṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The nature of the origin of the air</l>
<l>which starts from the navel</l>
<l>and the modifications which it undergoes</l>
<l>before it comes out as articulated speech in all sounds,</l>
<l>and of its quantity therein,</l>
<l>is clearly investigated and given</l>
<l>in the secret scriptures of the Antaṇar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
